                    <span>This book can give you basic knowledge which is helpful for new VB programmer on serial port communication. However, if you are trying to find sth related to RS485 communication, you will be disappointed becasue the example is no longer suitable nowadays. Try technical notes from device manufacturer on the web is a better solution.</span>
                  
