                    <span>This book is quite disappointing.  It's coverage is both narrow and  shallow.  If you're after some code to do serial programming from Visual Basic it's probably ok, but any different or deeper than that, you're better off with what you'll find on Google.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent companion to the PC parallel port.</div>
